clusterList.phrase: i was twelve years old the first time i walked on water
we sailed for about an hour and a half then decided to head in to avoid damaging the mast in a capsize but not before some radical downwind surfing
with a little practice the seals swam in the right direction 100 of the time
i had caught two waves and was heading out again when i spotted the shark circling about 30 metres away
i immediately paddled for shore as fast as i could
paddling on one side of the canoe and then the other keeps the boat going forward
this is my only my second time sailing this route dude
